%% Diagram: Sync queue happy path with optimistic UI
%% Type: sequenceDiagram
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant U as User
    participant App as App (UI thread)
    participant IDB as IndexedDB queue
    participant SW as Service Worker
    participant API as Server API

    U->>App: edit record
    App->>IDB: append SyncQueueItem
    App-->>U: optimistic UI update
    App->>SW: registration.sync.register("pending")

    Note over SW: connectivity returns
    SW->>IDB: read pending items (FIFO)
    SW->>API: POST /sync (idempotency-key)
    alt 2xx
        API-->>SW: ack + canonical record
        SW->>IDB: mark item synced
        SW->>App: postMessage("synced", id)
        App->>U: dismiss "saving..." badge
    else permanent 4xx
        API-->>SW: error code
        SW->>IDB: mark failed
        SW->>App: postMessage("conflict", id)
    else transient 5xx / offline
        SW-->>SW: throw -> browser retries on next sync event
    end
